title: EMMERDALE 25 TH FEBUARY 2008 TV RIP
description:
When Perdy turns her back, Katie grabs the keys from her purse and finds the green cardigan.

Perdy catches her, but Katie manages to convince her she only wants to help. Furthermore, Katie tells her she should destroy the evidence as it will only be a burden to her in the future.

Perdy falls for it hook, line and sinker. But no sooner than she&#039;s thrown the cardigan into the fire, Katie tells her the truth - that she and Grayson are in love and will soon be "one big, happy family."

Watch Perdy&#039;s reaction by clicking on the image above

Elsewhere, Laurel was livid when she walked into the cafe and saw Viv trying to raise money in Daniel&#039;s name.

And finally, Louise and Jamie went for a romantic hike in the hills. But Jamie lived to regret the idea.

RUNTIME 60 MINS
